When testing comment out line 27 to disable fullscreen mode.
Then to run the program use the below command

DISPLAY=:0 nohup /usr/bin/python3 photoframegtk.py

this detaches the process from the main terminal thread
so you can close the terminal without killing the process

To stop autostart remove:

sudo rm /etc/xdg/autostart/photo-frame-gtk-autostart.desktop
sudo reboot

To enable autostart run the RUN_THIS_ONE.sh script.